      </p>\r\n                <p class=\"item\">\r\n            <a href=\"https://www.heart-group.co.jp/recruit/coworker/2005-tu.html\" class=\"cardlink\">\r\n                <img src=\"https://www.heart-group.co.jp/recruit/.assets/futo4_sumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\">                <span>製造部門 平判製袋課 <span>T.Uさん</span></span>\r\n            </a>\r\n        </p>\r\n                <p class=\"item\">\r\n            <a href=\"https://www.heart-group.co.jp/recruit/coworker/2024-RK.html\" class=\"cardlink\">\r\n                <img src=\"https://www.heart-group.co.jp/recruit/.assets/%E2%98%86kabu7_main_thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\">                <span> 営業課 <span>R.Kさん</span></span>\r\n            </a>\r\n        </p>\r\n                <p class=\"item\">\r\n            <a href=\"https://www.heart-group.co.jp/recruit/coworker/2014-ch.html\" class=\"cardlink\">\r\n                <img src=\"https://www.heart-group.co.jp/recruit/.assets/futo1_sumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\">                <span>製造部門 仕上加工課 <span>C.Hさん</span></span>\r\n            </a>\r\n        </p>\r\n                <p class=\"item\">\r\n            <a href=\"https://www.heart-group.co.jp/recruit/coworker/2016-ry.html\" class=\"cardlink\">\r\n                <img src=\"https://www.heart-group.co.jp/recruit/.assets/kabu5_sumbnail-min.jpg\" alt=\"\">                <span> 営業課 <span>R.Yさん</span></span>\r\n            </a>\r\n        </p>\r\n                <p class=\"item\">\r\n            <a href=\"https://www.heart-group.co.jp/recruit/coworker/1997-kk.html\" class=\"cardlink\">\r\n                <img src=\"https://www.heart-group.co.jp/recruit/.assets/futo2_sumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\">                <span>製造部門 輪転製袋課 <span>K.Kさん</span></span>\r\n            </a>\r\n        </p>\r\n        </div>\r\n    <p class=\"link\"><a class=\"link1\" href=\"/recruit/coworker/\">すべてを見る</a></p>\r\n    \r\n                        </div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n\t\t\t</div><!-- .page-content -->\r\n\r\n    